Cell["\<\
Convert it to a full phase vector for the even parity. Note that the \
resulting vector is symmetric and involves a factor of 2 in the middle:\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->976627662,ExpressionUUID->"97b0f143-d070-4b2e-8714-92fde5199a54"],

